data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bed, 3 full bath, 2841sqft home in the Eagle Creek Golf Course Community that is only minutes away from the VA line.Enter into your wide foyer that has an extra room needed for that 5th bedroom or office directly located across the 2019 addition of a handicap accessible bathroom. Then make your way back through the welcoming great room with wood fireplace and enter into your large eat in kitchen that overlooks your in-ground salt water pool with views of a stocked pond. Upstairs you have a sizable primary bedroom with an en-suite that has vaulted ceilings, separate shower and tub, and dual sinks. Down the hall are three additional secondary bedrooms and a full bath.  Near OBX beaches, shopping, attractions and peaceful commute to many local military bases.
